result.title: Invitation to participate in INSCRIPTION 2014 — Programming Contest
result.content:
Hello Engineer 2014 — NIT Surathkal's annual techfest is the second largest technical event in south India and is known the brilliant set of events that it showcases every year.

Inscription is Engineer's premier event and one of India's biggest coding events. It is also the Flagship Event of Engineer's Comps Committee . With tons of participants from 15+ countries we manage to attract some the best coders of the world to compete for the prestigious event.

This year we are making it bigger, better and tougher . Following are the details of competition :

  1. Dates : 17th October

  2. Timings (CST) : 430am (17th) to 430pm (17th)

  3. Prizes : 25k INR = $400

  4. Contest Link : https://www.hackerrank.com/inscription2014 Please do register at the link.... We are looking forward to humongous participation in Inscription this year.

For more details check out https://www.facebook.com/INSCRIPTION2014 and https://www.facebook.com/events/791330444244243 .

Thanks..
